Installation
============

1) Install vim-plug
2) mkdir ~/.vim
3) cd ~/.vim
4) git clone
5) brew install nvim
6) pip install -r requirements.txt
7) touch ~/.config/nvim/init.vim
8) Enter following
```
set runtimepath^=~/.vim runtimepath+=~/.vim/after
let &packpath = &runtimepath
source ~/.vim/.vimrc
```
9) install nerdfonts for nerdtree icons to work properly
https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts
10) open nvim and run :PlugInstall
11) Select Nerd tree font from Preferences for fonts to correctly work with nerdtree
